'''Amisus''' was a [[Gender/Legends|female]] who was the daughter of the [[Ruurian/Legends|Ruurian]] [[S. V. Skynx/Legends|S. V. Skynx]]. She eventually became the leader of the [[Unified Ruurian Colonies]]. She pledged the support of the Ruurians to "[[Flim (Human)|Thrawn]]" during the [[Caamas Document Crisis]].

